title: Collection of Kade TBPs
description:
This is a collection of 7 TBPs about Arcana Studio's Kade, created by Sean O'Reilly. You can find more info here - http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kade_(comics). This torrent contains:

Original Sun (2004)
Shiva's Sun (2004)
Sun of Perdition (2006)
Rising Sun (2008)
Red Sun (2010)
Prodigal Sun (2011)
Mourning Sun (2012)

All credit to Digital Empire for the scans. Enjoy as always and please seed! :-)
